---
// Page 404 standalone — structure HTML complete, pas d'import Layout
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Page introuvable — Gigarun</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html, body { height: 100%; background-color: #07001C; color: #F1F0F7; font-family: 'Syne', system-ui, sans-serif; }
    body {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    body::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -100px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 800px; height: 500px; background: rgba(124,58,237,0.15); border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(140px); pointer-events: none;
    }
    body::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: -80px; right: -100px;
      width: 400px; height: 400px; background: rgba(6,182,212,0.08); border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(100px); pointer-events: none;
    }
    .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 600px; width: 100%; }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: #110833;
      border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.35); border-radius: 9999px; padding: 6px 16px;
      font-size: 13px; color: #9B99AA; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .badge-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #7C3AED; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; }
    .error-code {
      font-size: clamp(100px,20vw,160px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,#7C3AED,#06B6D4); -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -4px;
    }
    .title { font-size: clamp(22px,4vw,32px); font-weight: 700; color: #F1F0F7; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .subtitle { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #9B99AA; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 420px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .buttons { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: #7C3AED;
      color: #fff; font-family: 'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;
      padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 9999px; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #6D28D9; }
    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #F1F0F7;
      font-family: 'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;
      padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 9999px; text-decoration: none; transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
    .footer-note { margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(155,153,170,0.5); }
    .footer-note a { color: #7C3AED; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span>Erreur · Page introuvable</div>
    <div class="error-code">404</div>
    <h1 class="title">Page introuvable</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Cette page a peut-être été déplacée, supprimée ou n'a jamais existé.<br/>Même nos meilleurs techniciens ne l'ont pas trouvée.</p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary">
        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/></svg>
        Retour à l'accueil
      </a>
      <a href="/#services" class="btn-outline">
        Voir nos services
        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-note">Besoin d'aide ? <a href="mailto:contact@gigarun.net">contact@gigarun.net</a> · <a href="tel:+262692311191">0692 31 11 91</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
